<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="no-js">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">

  <!-- Mobile viewport optimization h5bp.com/ad -->
  <meta name="HandheldFriendly" content="True">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">

  <!-- Internet Explorer use the highest version available -->
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">

  <!-- Mobile IE allows us to activate ClearType technology for smoothing fonts for easy reading -->
  <!--[if IEMobile]>
  <meta http-equiv="cleartype" content="on">
  <![endif]-->

  <title><%= render_page_title %></title>
  <%= opensearch_description_tag application_name, opensearch_catalog_url(format: 'xml') %>
  <%= favicon_link_tag %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", media: "all" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= content_for(:head) %>
  <!-- Le HTML5 shim, for IE6-8 support of HTML5 elements -->
  <!--[if lt IE 9]>
  <script src="//html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"></script>
  <![endif]-->

</head>
<body class="<%= render_body_class %>" onload="checkCookie()">

<%= render :partial => 'shared/header_navbar' %>

<%= render partial: 'shared/ajax_modal' %>

<div id="main-container" class="<%= container_classes %>">
  <%= content_tag :h1, application_name, class: 'sr-only application-heading' %>

  <%= render :partial => '/flash_msg', layout: 'shared/flash_messages' %>

  <div id="content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-header">
        <div>
          <h2 class="page-heading"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span> Danmarks Breve søgetips</h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">

          <div id="om-dkbreve" class="document">
            <div class="text-content">
              <div class="text">

                <h1>Hvordan søger jeg?</h1>
                <p>Der kan søges frit i den fulde brevtekst, der kan søges på afsender, modtager og på brevets
                  afsendelsessted og modtagelsessted, og søgeresultaterne kan begrænses til et datospænd.</p>
                <h1></h1>
                <p></p>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<%= render :partial => 'shared/footer' %>
</body>
</html>




